Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.15,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.49,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Sup pasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:53.24,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Satu mangkuk hanya lapan tembaga kecil!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:56.07,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Pasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.16,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Ha? Budak, ni pertama kali\Nke kau datang ke bandar ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:00.58,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:05.25,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Pasta ala sup! Masakan ini menggunakan\Ngandum yang dipanggil "mi",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:09.00,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,yang dicipta oleh Liselotte-sama,\Nyang mana memerintah Amando.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.21,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Liselotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.38,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Ini masakan yang telah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.30,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Makasih menunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.97,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Pasta... {basically maggi}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.47,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Pertama kali aku\Nnampak di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:21.43,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dan dengar perkataan "mi".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:25.98,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Nampak lazat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.73,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Memang lazat pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.32,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, satu mangkuk, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.44,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Berehh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:37.91,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sedapnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.28,Utama,org kedai,0,0,0,,Kan! Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.83,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Rasanya yang nostalgik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:48.33,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan Liselotte ni juga datang dari dunia yang sama dengan Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.38,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Bukan penting pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.47,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau fikir tentang itu pun bukannya boleh buat apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:03.39,Haruto,Rio's mom,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bila kamu dah besar nanti, ibu akan\Nbawa kamu ke sana. Tempat bernama Yagumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.77,Haruto,Rio; 5 yo,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Betulkah? Ibu janji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.52,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:11.15,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku mahu melihat tempat asal ibu dan ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.65,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Itulah janji aku dengan ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.24,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Itu ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.74,Condong,org kedai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kamu nak beli mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:25.00,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ya. Saya rasa sesuai untuk perjalanan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.29,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ah, terima kasih atas makanannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:30.50,Condong,org kedai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kalau begitu, pergilah ke\NPersatuan Pedagang Rickka di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:34.17,Condong,org kedai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Terdapat barisan panjang\Ndi kedai menjuu di bawahnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.67,Condong,org kedai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}pasti kamu akan terus tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.51,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Menjuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:41.30,Condong,org kedai,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ya! Itu pun salah satu Liselotte-sama punya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.68,Utama,boy's mom,0,0,0,,Sedap kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.77,Utama,boy,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:47.48,Utama,manjuu shop,0,0,0,,Dua menjuu daging dan satu menjuu keju!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.85,Utama,manjuu shop,0,0,0,,Terima kasih kerana menunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.36,Utama,manjuu shop,0,0,0,,Ia masih panas, hati-hati, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.11,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Manjuu eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.11,NOTA,Rio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Manjuu = Lebih kurg mcm cekodok ade inti gituh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.32,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Terasa rindu pula.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.57,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Selamat datang ke Persatuan Pedagang Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.28,Kosette,Kosette,0,0,0,,{\fs70}Terima kasih banyak-banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.91,Kosette,Kosette,0,0,0,,{\fs70}Silalah datang lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.45,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Tuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:10.38,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Kami minta agar kamu tidak\Nmembawa pedang masuk ke dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.46,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Kalau mahu, kami boleh jagakan\Nbarang kamu sementara itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.21,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.42,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Rambut hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.89,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baiklah, tolong, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:24.39,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Terima kasih kerana memberikan kerjasama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:28.77,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Saya akan membantu kamu\Nhari ini. Nama saya Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.83,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.24,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Maaf mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.62,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Terima kasih kerana menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:51.92,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Lima belas kilo pasta kering\Ndan sepuluh kilo barli.{restraining myself from writing MAGGI}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.75,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Saya juga sudah menyiapkan\Nperkakas dan rempah masakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.67,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Oh yakah? Terima kasih banyak-banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:04.10,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Saya sudah tambahkan beg sandar,\Ntapi ianya sangat berat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.18,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Bolehkah kamu boleh membawanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.14,Kosette,Kosette,0,0,0,,Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.35,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:13.48,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya ada banyak berlatih fizikal, jadi janganlah risau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.94,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Adakah kamu biasa minum teh hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.49,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Seorang gadis yang saya kenal\Nsangat sukakan teh hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.25,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya belajar banyak perkara\Nsemasa minum bersama dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:34.00,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, jangan-jangan kamu\Nboleh cam jenis daun teh ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.96,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aroma yang unik dan sedikit masam-manis...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:44.01,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Adakah ini daun teh dari Risu?\NKamu guna teh yang berkualiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.76,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Cawan ini juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:49.06,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Untuk mendapatkan tawaran yang\Nterbaik dengan pelanggan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.77,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,suasana urusan perlulah sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.81,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Itulah moto persatuan kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:07:00.78,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Lepastu... boleh kita teruskan urusan \Npenghantaran surat untuk kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.78,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:07.53,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dengan itu, saya telah selesai\Nmembeli-belah, dan bertolak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:11.33,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Setelah saya keluar dari daerah Strahl,\Nsaya sudah tidak boleh lagi menghantar surat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.96,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,tapi janganlah risau.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.96,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau tiada berita itu maksudnya saya baik-baik sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:17.96,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:19.13,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.92,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Jaga diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.80,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih kerana membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:32.23,Kosette,Kosette,0,0,0,,Remaja itu agak misteri kan, Liselotte-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:35.60,Lotte,Lotte,0,0,0,,Tapi Kosette, sekarang ni saya Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.48,Kosette,Kosette,0,0,0,,Haah kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.11,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Budak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.37,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Hei, kamu tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.30,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Racun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.14,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Manusia jadian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.10,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Engkau...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.94,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ku bunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.40,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku mesti neutralkan racun ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:30.32,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Maaf. Tapi aku tak boleh\Nbiarkan kau membunuh aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.71,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Racun... Tiada kesan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.92,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Laju!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.60,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(960,940)\fscy62\fscx66}Sihir Penguat Kebolehan Fizikal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.60,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enchant Physical Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:54.43,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dia belum lagi meguatkan\Nkebolehan fizikal dia dengan sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.68,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi gerakan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.69,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Berapa laju agaknya dia selepas ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:09.32,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenapa... Kenapa orang ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.41,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dia hanyalah manusia.\NTetapi sangat pantas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.93,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dia terlalu fokus kepada pisaunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.49,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sampai sini sahaja. Faham?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.41,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,T-Tak... Tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.99,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya tak nak mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:59.58,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,O-Oi! Bertenang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.25,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,T-Tolong saya! Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.96,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:07.67,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak ada cara lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.06,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tali Leher Perhambaan? {Kolar Penyerahan}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.57,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Sihir dalam buku itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.32,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,{\pos(904.026,940)\fscy62\fscx66}Nyahjampi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.32,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dispell, kan? {lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.41,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau aku tiru semula, boleh cabut ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:54.30,Condong,Stewart; aged 6,0,0,0,,Hoi, Latifa! Bangun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.14,Condong,Stewart,0,0,0,,Latifa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.02,Latifa,Latifa; 4 tahun,0,0,0,,{\fs70}Latifa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:07.69,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Nama saya Endo Suzune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.57,Condong,Stewart,0,0,0,,Kau mamai mende?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.33,Condong,Stewart,0,0,0,,Latifa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.04,Condong,Stewart,0,0,0,,Siapa aku bagi kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.04,Condong,Stewart,0,0,0,,Stewart onii-sama.{euww wtf... EUWWWWW WTFFFF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:28.96,NOTA,Stewart,0,0,0,,Onii = Abang; Sama = Gelaran hormat. {Aku tak tau nak letak melayunya apa}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.96,Condong,Stewart,0,0,0,,Cepat, cakap "Onii-sama"! {wtf dude eeuuwww}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.01,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,T-Tak... Tak nak—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:39.18,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Sakit! Sakit! Sakit!{yo talented giler seiyuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.47,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,{\fscy84\fscx84}Sakit! Sakit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.68,Condong,Stewart,0,0,0,,"Onii-sama." Cakap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.85,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,O-Onii-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.69,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Oi. Bangun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.78,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Cukup. Tangan dan kaki kau dah terikat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:01.29,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Nampaknya kau faham situasi sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:04.37,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau kau tak nak mati,\Njangan mengganas macam tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:10.13,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Kalau saya tak melawan,\Nkamu tak akan bunuh saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.09,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Itu semua bergantung pada kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.55,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kau datang dari Beltrant ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.26,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.47,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kau tahu apa benda ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.31,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,T... Tali leher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.35,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Dah... Tak ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.48,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:31.61,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kamu mengikut arahan kerana tali leher ini, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.28,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kau dah tak akan disakiti lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:53.63,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Memandangkan tali leher sudah tiada,\Nkau tiada masalah untuk jawab persoalan aku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.05,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Siapa yang memerintahkan kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:02.64,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Hanya aku dan kau disini. Jangan risau.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:06.73,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,S-Saya tak tahu nama tuan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.52,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya tak pernah diberitahu, jadinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.56,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Nama keluarga pun kau tak tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.65,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Nama keluarga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.40,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,T-Tapi, saya tahu nama abang saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.61,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Dia cakap, Stewart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:24.62,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Stewart... Adakah dia manusia jadian seperti kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.54,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Abang saya manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.87,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Manusia yang melatih saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.13,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Manusia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.88,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dah agak, pasti dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:37.01,Condong,Stewart,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Pesalahnya adalah budak setinggan tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.59,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Khuatir akan kebenarannya terserlah,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:43.01,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Datuk Huguenot cuba untuk\Nmelenyapkan aku. Bila difikirkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.81,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,masuk akal juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:50.44,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ada sesiapa lagi selain kau\Nyang cuba membunuh aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.06,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya tak tahu-desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:56.73,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Tapi saya rasa tak ada... Mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.03,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.95,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Soalan terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:05.03,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kau masih lagi nak bunuh aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.12,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya tak nak bunuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.58,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ha, lantak kau lah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.38,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku tinggalkan kelengkapan\Npada kau jubah di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:22.39,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Mulai sekarang, kau boleh larikan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.72,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Memandangkan tali leher yang\Nmengawal kau sudah tiada,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.39,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,tak perlulah kau kembali\Nsemula kepada tuan kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:34.40,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi, dekat Strahl, yang mana\Nmanusia jadian dijadikan hamba,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.19,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,tiada tempat yang selamat untuk dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.40,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau kau keluar negara ini\Ndan menuju ke timur,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.99,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,terdapat kawasan luas\Ndikenali sebagai Belantara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.95,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Di tempat itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:50.62,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,pasti terdapat tempat di mana manusia jadian\Nseperti kau dan yang lain tinggal bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:54.42,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Hutan Belantara? Timur...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:57.25,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ke arah perjalanan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.21,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Daripada tinggal di sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.93,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,lebih baik kau cari rakan sejenis untuk hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:06.97,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Rakan sejenis. Timur. Hutan Belantara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.60,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku gerak dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:14.31,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Satut lagi, kalau kau serang aku lepas ini,\Naku tak akan teragak-agak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.83,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa lagi yang kau nak dari aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:31.50,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,E-Err, timur...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:34.58,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya juga, bersama, ingin pergi-desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.09,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Mungkin kau salah faham.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:42.80,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku bukannya merdekakan kau\Nkerana ingin menyelamatkan kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:48.10,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Cuma supaya kau tak cuba\Nuntuk membunuh aku. Itu sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:52.73,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,T-Tapi... Saya tak tahu apa yang saya perlu buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:58.15,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku ini manusia, sebangsa dengan orang\Nyang jadikan kau hamba, tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.73,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kau tak takut?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.99,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Kamu tak nampak... jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:08.95,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kau ingat aku tak rasa apa-apa\Nselepas kau cuba membunuh aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.12,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,M-Maafkan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:19.21,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku bukanlah marah ke apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:22.21,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kau pun tak boleh\Ningkar perintah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:27.38,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi, boleh jadi kau akan cuba serang aku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.76,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Pendek kata, aku tak percaya kau. Faham tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:36.10,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, t-tali leher!\NPakaikan pada saya! Tak mengapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:39.52,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Tak mengapa! Saya mohon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.02,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,K-Kenapa kau bawa benda itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.90,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kau kan benci dipakaikan tali leher tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:49.82,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya lagi benci... Keseorangan... Seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.24,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fscx90}Saya takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.91,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya mohon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:58.29,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baik, ikut suka hati kau lah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.38,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ah, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.92,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak-banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.92,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Pergi buang tali leher itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.55,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:06.13,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.55,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa nama kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:12.10,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Latifa-desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.31,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ooo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.77,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.06,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Salam perkenalan ya, Latifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.90,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Baiklah...desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:30.53,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,M-Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.33,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kamu tak perlu minta maaf\Nkerana perkara kecil sebegitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.20,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.45,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya boleh makan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.83,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya. Jangan malu-malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:46.21,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Sedapnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.26,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kan. {Malay 'kan'}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:55.31,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak ada siapa akan ambil.\NMakanlah dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:18:01.48,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Hidangan saya... makanan haiwan...\NSetiap hari, abang saya akan...{fak u stewart, nak cari fasal dgn nekomimi, langkah mayatku dulu!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.74,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kita dah nak sampai ke Hutan Belantara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.62,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kamu boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.53,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya tak mengapa-desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.12,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kita sudah melepasi sempadan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.37,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Masih awal lagi, tapi mari kita bekhemah di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.54,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Maafkan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.09,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu minta maaf pula?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.76,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Sebab saya menyusahkan kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.26,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak adalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:37.81,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.89,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Ini surat dari Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.31,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baguslah, dia baik-baik sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.69,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Tiba di Amando dalam masa\Ntiga hari sahaja, lajunya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.48,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Mungkin agak sunyi sedikit\Ntak dapat khabar dari dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:53.20,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,951)}Tapi semoga, perjalanan kamu baik-baik sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.62,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Wah! Spageti?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.71,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh, kamu tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:05.04,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ya! Spageti-desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.00,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Boleh saya makan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.42,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,H-Ha.{asian ha}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.38,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya... makan dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.22,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kamu pernah makan pasta sebelum ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.14,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:24.85,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ah, err... Ya, saya rasa pernah\Nmakan-desu. Mungkin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.23,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Yakah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.57,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ingatkan kamu dah biasa makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.86,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ada banyak lagi.\NMakanlah puas-puas, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.82,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Terima kasih-desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:38.12,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Memanggil pasta sebagai "spageti", maksudnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:41.04,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan, dia ini juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.84,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh, kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:51.13,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya tak suka! Dekat mana ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.63,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya mahu balik ke rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:20:00.43,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Janganlah risau ya. Dah tak menakutkan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:04.27,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ibu, Ayah, Onii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.81,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya mahu pulang ke Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.31,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:13.36,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak syak lagi. Budak ini juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.28,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Onii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.45,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Bertenanglah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:41.05,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Rambut dia... Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.97,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Seiras dengan dia, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.31,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.06,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi. Semalam kamu dapat tidur?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.61,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kamu tak apa-apa ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:58.11,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ya, Onii... Rio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.03,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Oni... Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.83,NOTA,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau satu harakat je, jadi Iblis/Syaitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.83,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,B-Bukanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:06.21,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya nak sebut "Onii-chan", lepas tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:11.00,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Kalau saya panggil Rio-san, Onii-chan, boleh? {insert Sagiri seiyuu meme :kekw:}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:11.71,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.88,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Tak boleh ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:16.26,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Bukannya tak boleh..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:20.47,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ibu, Ayah, Onii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.97,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya nak balik Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.31,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Budak ini masih lagi kecil lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:29.56,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,dihidupkan kembali dari Bumi\Nke dunia ini dan diperhambakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:31.65,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dia pasti sangat kesunyian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:35.48,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau ini boleh menenangkan\Ndia walaupun sedikit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:55.59,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:57.88,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Hari ini kita sarapan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.84,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa kamu mahu makan, Latifa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:02.80,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,{\pos(999.529,1011)}Saya mahu telur dadar\Nbeserta keju di dalamnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.93,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Telur dadar? Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.10,Utama,boy,0,0,0,,Hei, Latifa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:14.73,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kamu memang tak nampak\Npokok besar di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:18.65,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Yang kamu kata semalam ke?\NSaya hanya nampak hutan biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:21.99,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Latifa tak boleh melihatnya. Maksudnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:25.33,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Adakah ia dihalang dari pandangan\Nmanusia melalui sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:28.62,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:31.92,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Betul ke kita nak masuk ke sana?\NTak sesat ke nanti?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:33.13,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Jangan risaulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.59,0:22:41.26,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, saya terbau samar-samar\Nsesuatu yang saya tak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:42.51,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Lebih dari satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:44.72,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baunya berbeza dari bau haiwan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:45.72,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:51.27,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Memandangkan ia samar-samar,\Npasti ianya berdekatan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.15,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Saya rasa, mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.15,0:22:56.90,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, apa kata kita\Nberehat di sini hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:22:59.65,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Mungkin tujuan kita sudah dekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:01.19,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Betulkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.57,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Akhirnya kita boleh keluar dari hutan, kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.42,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dia masih bermimpi buruk lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:20.26,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dengan ini, dia tak akan bermimpi buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:32.68,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1044.838)}Apa!
